Radical Blog

An example project built on the Radical-PHP framework.

Aim: To build a blogging system in less than 1,000 lines of code.

Features:
 - HTML Post support   [ ]
 - Comments            [ ]
 - AntiSpam            [ ]
 - Captcha             [ ]
 - Tags and Categories [*]
 - Search              [*]
 - Admin panel         [ ]
 - Form validation     [ ]
 - WYSIWYG editor      [ ]
 - Theme               [*]
 
 Radical-PHP: https://github.com/splitice/radical-php